meta_data.description: After finishing No. 2 on last year’s list of the world’s highest-paid comedians, Jerry Seinfeld returns to the top this year.  While no one could out-earn the king of comedy, here's who else made the $15 million cut. The World's Highest-Paid Comedians 2017 - pg.1
meta_data.author: Rebecca Lerner
